The '''''Jump For Joy''''' was a [[Twomi Skyfire]] on [[Utharis]] in [[17 ABY/Legends|17 ABY]]. [[Akanah Norand Goss Pell|Akanah]] had intentions of stealing it until the captain confronted her outside of his ship, where he would ask her if she had ever had intercourse while in [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]].

